{"tid":711451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主共和兩黨：比起支持美軍，Google似乎更願意支持中國共產黨","createTime":"2018-06-21T14:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T14:17:55.000Z","uid":11001,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b030eb50cfdae01efbf7331ec2255c50b7df3373","tid":711451,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:10:33.000Z","msg":"美國民主、共和兩黨的議員在周三向Google行政總裁Sundar Pichai發信，要求Google重新考慮與華為的合作關係，並警告與華為的合作有可能構成嚴重國家安全風險。<br />\n<br />\n該信件由共和黨參議員Tom Cotton、Marco Rubio，共和黨眾議員Michael Conaway和Liz Cheney，以及民主黨眾議員Dutch Ruppersberger共同發出。<br />\n<br />\n兩黨在信中關注到，Google早前退出與美國國防部合作的人工智能研究項目「Project Maven」，但另一方面卻與華為保持著戰略合作夥伴關係，「我們很遺憾Google不想繼續保持軍方和科技公司之間悠久而富有成果的合作傳統，更令人失望的是，比起支持美軍，Google似乎更願意支持中國共產黨」。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle發言人回應指，Google與許多美國公司一樣，都與全球包括華為在內數以十計的生產商達成協議。「在這些協議中，我們並沒有容許進入Google用戶數據的特別權限，協議內容包含私隱與用戶數據安全保障。」<br />\n<br />\n華為作為目前全球第三大智能手機製造商，一直與Google有緊密的合作。除了讓華為手機使用Google的Android作業系統之外，今年一月雙方更宣布組成戰略合作夥伴，發展獨有的短訊傳送系統。<br />\n<br />\n華為近期屢被質疑涉及間諜活動。美國國會「美中經濟與安全審查委員會」早前發布報告，指中國政府可能支持某些企業進行間諜活動，以提高中企競爭力並促進政府利益，報告特別點名華為、中興通訊、聯想三家企業。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人華春瑩今年四月回應事件時，反批美國以國家安全之名，行貿易保護主義之實。她反問若美國有人買了華為手機就被視為威脅國家安全，美國是否脆弱到如此地步。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E5%85%A9%E9%BB%A8%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%A1google-%E6%89%B9%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1-%E5%A4%9A%E6%96%BC%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D-%E4%BF%83%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E8%88%87%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%2585%25A9%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25BF%25A1google-%25E6%2589%25B9%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%2596%25BC%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25BB%258D-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25BF%2582%2F&d=rKuEXMB5T1WbgDAVYwUu1f7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=c35aaf59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%2585%25A9%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25BF%25A1google-%25E6%2589%25B9%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%2596%25BC%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25BB%258D-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25BF%2582%2F&h=3dbbe3dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E5%85%A9%E9%BB%A8%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%A1google-%E6%89%B9%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1-%E5%A4%9A%E6%96%BC%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D-%E4%BF%83%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E8%88%87%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82/</a>"},{"pid":"c4c4200267c704ae610b40bb0f15162752bfa136","tid":711451,"uid":149902,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:13:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67fd4157305615986ca86fb0474b30896f5c53d3","tid":711451,"uid":54733,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:24:28.000Z","msg":"Marco Rubio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e945202820187873e607fe4599fd4588432d2c4b","tid":711451,"uid":106363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:28:33.000Z","msg":"究竟最後google會贏定係共產黨會贏?"},{"pid":"c5ee680d9ac31395f308f8680bd63fd463ffe3fc","tid":711451,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e945202820187873e607fe4599fd4588432d2c4b","tid":711451,"uid":106363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:28:33.000Z","msg":"究竟最後google會贏定係共產黨會贏?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:30:19.000Z","msg":